    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40401040_41_1424-1472",
      "chapterUid": 41,
      "range": "1424-1472",
      "markText": "老师教给我，要学骆驼，沉得住气的动物。看它从不着急，慢慢的走，慢慢的嚼；总会走到的，总会吃饱的。",
      "totalCount": 4329,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40401040&chapterUid=41&rangeStart=1424&rangeEnd=1472",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4b232610726878904b220c8?chapterUid=41&rangeStart=1424&rangeEnd=1472"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40401040_50_2878-2915",
      "chapterUid": 50,
      "range": "2878-2915",
      "markText": "“你呀——我猜不出，”我摇摇头，但又忽然想起来了：“你是不是来这里拉屎？”",
      "totalCount": 4122,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40401040&chapterUid=50&rangeStart=2878&rangeEnd=2915",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4b232610726878904b220c8?chapterUid=50&rangeStart=2878&rangeEnd=2915"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40401040_69_4795-4821",
      "chapterUid": 69,
      "range": "4795-4821",
      "markText": "“记住，你是吃饭长大，读书长大，也是在爱里长大的！”",
      "totalCount": 2768,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40401040&chapterUid=69&rangeStart=4795&rangeEnd=4821",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/4b232610726878904b220c8?chapterUid=69&rangeStart=4795&rangeEnd=4821"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40401040_52_537-597",
      "chapterUid": 52,
      "range": "537-597",
      "markText": "对了，我将来要写一本书，我要把天和海分清楚，我要把好人和坏人分清楚，我要把疯子和贼子分清楚，但是我现在却是什么也分不清。",
